      • getEmbeddedSolrServer

        public static org.apache.solr.client.solrj.embedded.EmbeddedSolrServer getEmbeddedSolrServer(String solrConfigXml,
                                                                                             String schemaXml,
                                                                                             ConfigurationFileProxy givenConfigFileProxy)
        Provides an already instantiated SolrClient object. If an instance has not already been instantiated, then the single instance will be instantiated with the provided configuration file. If an instance already exists, it cannot be overwritten with a new configuration.
        Parameters:
        solrConfigXml - the name of the solr configuration filename such as solrconfig.xml
        schemaXml - filename of the schema such as schema.xml
        givenConfigFileProxy - a ConfigurationFileProxy instance. If instance is null, a new ConfigurationFileProxy is used instead.
        Returns:
        SolrClient instance
